{"tid":2302419,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"安巴比譴責警暴","createTime":"2020-11-27T06:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T07:14:00.000Z","uid":78243,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf425496943367e0944952d46f4baff2f39a47d","tid":2302419,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】巴黎聖日耳門球星安巴比周四與法國國家隊隊友和其他運動員，一起譴責警察被拍到在巴黎毆打黑人音樂製作人，並稱該短片令人無法忍受。<br />\n安巴比（Kylian Mbappe）在Twitter貼上受傷的製作人米歇爾的照片，並寫道，「無法忍受的影片，無法接受的暴力。對種族主義說不。」他這個Twitter被迅速轉發了12.5萬次以上。<br />\n<br />\n過去，法國運動員通常不願公開表示政治立場，這與美國運動員大力支持「Black Lives Matter」不同，但是這種情況似乎引起了共鳴，並且越來越多的知名人士發聲。<br />\n<br />\n另一位法國球星賓祖文文迪也在社交媒體上貼相表示，「誰保護我們免受警察襲擊？如果沒有影片，米歇爾會怎樣？他們是否傾向相信警察的證供嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n米歇爾最初因暴力和不服從警察而被捕，但是檢察官沒有進行調查，而是對警察進行了調查。3名警察已被停職，還有第4人被指控向事件發生的音樂工作室投擲催淚彈，據說是因為米歇爾沒有戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=31504394192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D31504394192&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpNToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=0a9629f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=31504394192</a>"},{"pid":"6b4bc0fce7736797506d50565a173a25c59ade45","tid":2302419,"uid":141656,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd902432bb262cf434969b9097bf06a1a5ab0af","tid":2302419,"uid":16034,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"還有第4人被指控向事件發生的音樂工作室投擲催淚彈，據說是因為米歇爾沒有戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個人中過武肺?"},{"pid":"9307878450d3ea06478731ceebef3b8441888921","tid":2302419,"uid":62343,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"另一位法國<span class=\"red\">球星</span>賓祖文文迪也在社交媒體上貼相表示，「誰保護我們免受警察襲擊？如果沒有影片，米歇爾會怎樣？他們是否傾向相信警察的證供嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30ff29321aa58c29fbcb528568677fe5fafa9d9","tid":2302419,"uid":10290,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"都幾難癲捉人入屋打<br />\n俾其他人發現屌走<br />\n直接掟gas入你屋<br />\n你當法國係香港咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d5f57ab1d9a0687806885fdac16df6f4353edc","tid":2302419,"uid":213841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"真球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c80e54d92e7f6fa22d880ad8c211fa852b2889","tid":2302419,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好黃"},{"pid":"d55bc19d13819db5915ea78a5bdb0c6f669e71c4","tid":2302419,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"負評師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90935f90dbf461494b7a0892313ce540a04d1d48","tid":2302419,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"法國手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}